track_notes: Park near the cattle grid, lots of room. This is the shortest way up to NP-006 from the highest public road nearest the summit, it takes 40-50 minutes to reach the top. It is very boggy around Grimy Gutter Hags, if wet it may pay to walk alongside to the east a few 100m by the fence - marked on the 25000 map as dots.
track_title: G/NP-006 Great Shunner Fell from cattle grid at top of Buttertubs Pass
